'''Theon&amp;#39;s master of hounds''' is an unnamed minor character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by guest star [[Steve Wilson]] and only appears in &quot;[[A Man Without Honor]].&quot;

sections.Biography:
===[[Season 2]]===
The master of hounds assists [[Theon Greyjoy]] in the search for the escaped [[Bran Stark|Bran]] and [[Rickon Stark]]. They track them to a shepherd's farm where the hounds lose the scent of the boys. Theon later returns to [[Winterfell]] with the charred corpses of two children.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[A Man Without Honor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

Theon's crew turn on him and deliver him to [[Ramsay Snow]] in exchange for being allowed to leave Winterfell alive.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Valar Morghulis]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; However, they are betrayed by Snow, captured and flayed alive.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Mhysa]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
